details.comment: The official bracket lists Unknown522 as playing Adam in Losers Round 1. However, VODs show that Unknown522 played th0rn. This is also backed up by their final placements (Unknown522 in 33rd, th0rn in 25th),<ref>[https://smashboards.com/threads/official-pound-4-melee-results-thread.262154/ Pound 4 Results Thread]</ref> and by a later VOD of th0rn vs Zhu.<ref>[https://youtu.be/4BMJTtQr-uA Zhu vs th0rn Game 1]</ref> Consequently, th0rn and Adam have been switched on this bracket.
The recording of game 3 is incomplete, but the video description states that PC Chris won by 1 stock.
The order of matches is unknown.
